# Per-project workspaces — entire projects/ folder is gitignored by default.
# Each project is the producer's personal workspace (bibles, references, clips,
# audio, QC reports). Not for public sharing. If you want to commit an example
# project to the repo intentionally, use `git add -f projects/<name>/...`
projects/

